data.description: A well-cared-for home boasts charm and functionality.  5BR/4.2 bath+2 add'l carpeted & heated bonus rooms on the 3rd floor. Each BR has a walk-in closet, 9ft ceilings, & hardwood floors throughout. Chef's dream kitchen w/custom cabinetry, granite counters, HUGE pantry. Designed for multi-generational living ADU w/its own private entry. The dog kennel/barn has hot water and is fully fenced.
